2. Why are methods on the prototype?
3. Why is JS inheritance sharing instead of copying?
4. Difference between static and instance?
5. Why are arrow-function fields discouraged?
6. Difference between super() and super.method()?
7. Why does instanceof return true for parent classes?
8. Why can't subclasses access #private?
